<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Institutional Portfolios & Requests | Veteran Loan Servicing</title>
    <style>
        :root { --bg-main: #ffffff; --bg-card: #f8fafc; --gold-accent: #92400e; --navy-dark: #0f172a; --text-muted: #475569; --border-light: #e2e8f0; }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif; background: var(--bg-main); color: var(--navy-dark); line-height: 1.6; }
        header { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light); position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1000; }
        .nav-container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .logo { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; color: var(--navy-dark); text-transform: uppercase; }
        .logo span { color: var(--gold-accent); }
        .form-split-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 40px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 140px auto 60px auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        .form-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-light); padding: 35px; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; }
        .form-card h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--navy-dark); }
        .form-card p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 18px; }
        .name-row { display: flex; gap: 15px; }
        .name-row .form-group { flex: 1; }
        label { display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--navy-dark); }
        input, textarea { width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; background: #ffffff; }
        button { background: var(--gold-accent); color: white; border: none; padding: 14px 24px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; width: 100%; font-size: 1rem; transition: background 0.2s; }
        button:hover { background: #78350f; }
        .alt-btn { background: var(--navy-dark); }
        .alt-btn:hover { background: #1e293b; }
        footer { background: #f8fafc; padding: 40px 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light); text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="index.html" class="logo">Veteran <span>Loan Servicing</span></a>
            <a href="index.html" style="color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.95rem;">&larr; Return Home</a>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <main class="form-split-grid">
        <div class="form-card" style="border-top: 4px solid var(--gold-accent);">
            <div>
                <h2>Institutional Portfolio Onboarding Request</h2>
                <p>Provide preliminary details regarding your asset class pool, total lines under administration, and regional footprint to receive an operational onboarding brief within one business day.</p>
                
                <form action="https://formspree.io/f/PLACEHOLDER" method="POST">
                    <div class="name-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>First Name *</label>
                            <input type="text" name="First Name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Last Name *</label>
                            <input type="text" name="Last Name" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Institutional Email *</label>
                        <input type="email" name="Email" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Asset Pool Parameters & Footprint *</label>
                        <textarea rows="4" name="Onboarding Message" required placeholder="Specify lines under management, asset types..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit">Send Request</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-card" style="border-top: 4px solid var(--navy-dark);">
            <div>
                <h2>Follow for Industry Updates</h2>
                <p>Sign up to receive timely regulatory briefings, default timeline strategy adjustments, and private credit yield risk mitigation research alerts directly.</p>
                
                <form action="https://formspree.io/f/PLACEHOLDER" method="POST">
                    <div class="name-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>First Name *</label>
                            <input type="text" name="First Name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Last Name *</label>
                            <input type="text" name="Last Name" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Email Address *</label>
                        <input type="email" name="Email" required>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="alt-btn" style="margin-top: 10px;">Submit Registration</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Veteran Loan Servicing. All rights reserved. | <a href="privacy.html" style="color: var(--gold-accent); text-decoration: none;">Privacy Policy</a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
